originalText.text: This space gets great sunlight during the day, which energizes me and makes it easy to work.  The open floor plan enhances that energy, its always populated with positive people.  The outdoor patio is pretty cool as well!

originalText.text: I’ve been looking for a dedicated desk at a co-work space for a while and after visiting numerous offices I found 11desk and decided on the spot to make it my permanent office. It is airy, bright and beutifully designed and decorated. The office is equipped with everything I need from a projector for video conferences to high speed internet and the lounge area is perfect for meeting with customers. It also has its own terrace!! It’s a rare find in a commmercial building and you can not beat the location nor the price! I recommend 11desk to any entrepreneur who is looking for an affordable and comfortable co-work space in the heart of the city.
